    <item>
      <title>巴克莱银行和德意志银行将保留部分 FNZ 贷款</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-07/barclays-deutsche-among-banks-forced-to-hold-chunk-of-fnz-loan</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于未能筹集到足够的利息将全部贷款出售给投资者，包括巴克莱银行和德意志银行在内的多家银行不得不持有金融科技公司 FNZ 集团有限公司 21 亿美元再融资交易的大部分股份。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-07/barclays-deutsche-among-banks-forced-to-hold-chunk-of-fnz-loan</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 Nov 2024 13:24:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧洲央行行长对欧元区经济前景持乐观态度</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-07/ecb-s-knot-is-optimistic-on-outlook-for-euro-zone-economy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行管理委员会委员克拉斯·诺特表示，随着通胀趋缓和借贷成本下降，他对该地区经济前景感到乐观。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-07/ecb-s-knot-is-optimistic-on-outlook-for-euro-zone-economy</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 Nov 2024 13:10:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国央行降息并警告预算通胀压力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-07/boe-delivers-rate-cut-with-warning-of-budget-s-inflation-impact</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国央行今年第二次下调借贷成本，但没有暗示将加快宽松政策，并警告称预算可能导致通胀上升多达半个百分点。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-07/boe-delivers-rate-cut-with-warning-of-budget-s-inflation-impact</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 Nov 2024 12:00:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>对德国债务狂潮的担忧首次成为关键市场指标</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-07/fear-of-german-debt-binge-flips-key-market-gauge-for-first-time</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在财政保守派领袖、财政部长克里斯蒂安·林德纳 (Christian Lindner) 被解职后，交易员们为德国可能出售更多债券做好了准备，这导致一些市场人士开始考虑一个可能对高债务更加容忍的新政府。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-07/fear-of-german-debt-binge-flips-key-market-gauge-for-first-time</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 Nov 2024 09:31:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
